{"type":"message","id":"54101ff8","parentId":"d7faafe3","timestamp":"2026-04-06T01:01:08.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what skills are installed. I can see from the available_skills section in the system prompt that there are many skills listed. Let me provide a summary of them.","thinkingSignature":"a21857cd27f26e0611dede016a9f2c5b3d4a5c570ac5b3901977f08fcd785aa8"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 已安装的 Skills：\n\n**飞书系列**\n- `feishu-bitable` - 飞书多维表格管理\n- `feishu-calendar` - 飞书日历与日程\n- `feishu-channel-rules` - 飞书频道输出规则\n- `feishu-create-doc` - 创建飞书云文档\n- `feishu-fetch-doc` - 获取飞书云文档内容\n- `feishu-im-read` - 飞书消息读取\n- `feishu-task` - 飞书任务管理\n- `feishu-troubleshoot` - 飞书插件问题排查\n- `feishu-update-doc` - 更新飞书云文档\n- `飞书多 Agent 配置助手` - 多 Agent 系统配置\n\n**工具类**\n- `clawflow` - 任务流运行时\n- `clawflow-inbox-triage` - 收件箱分流示例\n- `clawhub` - Skill 市场 CLI\n- `coding-agent` - 编码 Agent 委托\n- `gemini` - Gemini CLI\n- `github` - GitHub 操作\n- `healthcheck` - 主机安全检查\n- `node-connect` - 节点连接诊断\n- `skill-creator` - Skill 创建工具\n- `skill-vetter` - Skill 安全审查\n- `summarize` - URL/文件摘要\n- `weather` - 天气查询\n- `vibesurf` - 浏览器自动化\n- `Agent Browser` - Rust 无头浏览器\n- `multi-search-engine` - 多引擎搜索\n- `self-improvement` - 自我改进\n- `openclaw-doctor` - OpenClaw 诊断工具\n\n共 **27 个 Skills**。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":412,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":12574,"totalTokens":13025,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0004944,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00471525,"total":0.00522135}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775437257859,"responseId":"062238ca95b8cdf876e05e4d31dd51d1"}}
