{"type":"message","id":"a8edf280","parentId":"da2d5f9e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T01:52:00.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OpenClaw is still on version 2026.4.2, and the status says \"up to date\". But the update command failed earlier. It seems the \"up to date\" message is from the update check, not an actual successful update.\n\nLet me report back to the user what happened:\n\n1. `openclaw update` tried to update but failed with npm ENOTEMPTY errors\n2. OpenClaw is still at 2026.4.2\n3. Skills couldn't be updated either due to registry issues\n\nLet me summarize this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"a83f749f1f10a1d04aebccf0a96c6b8c97c18414704e6c50cac457532e049f29"},{"type":"text","text":"更新检查结果：\n\n**OpenClaw 本身**\n- 当前版本：2026.4.2\n- `openclaw update` 尝试更新失败 → npm ENOTEMPTY 目录冲突\n- 手动 `npm install -g openclaw` 也因网络/超时中断\n- OpenClaw 状态显示 \"up to date\"，但实际是更新检查失败时的残留状态\n\n**Skills 更新**\n- `clawhub update --all` 失败 → 镜像源 registry 报 \"Skill not found\"（可能缺货或网络问题）\n- 多个 skill 显示 \"local changes (no match)\"，无法匹配远程版本\n\n**结论**\n1. OpenClaw 全局更新有目录锁定问题，需要手动清理后重试\n2. 镜像源对部分 skill 支持不完整\n\n要继续尝试修复 OpenClaw 更新吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15026,"output":298,"cacheRead":12509,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27833,"cost":{"input":0.0045078,"output":0.00035759999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00075054,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00561594}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775440309885,"responseId":"062244b6f30622ea14b0cc0467705b44"}}
